name: Last CriptoBurguer Experience: WTF? This is a "SANDWI(T)CH"
description:
"Join me and sing the spell
So a burger you'll feel the smell
Take the pickles and a cheese's slice
Throw them here and mix them twice
Let the fire burn and the potion boil
There's no need of fat or any oil
Take the sauce and take the bread
Throw them now for the hunger be dead
Lets dance around the fire
So the bubbles can make you inspired
This is how we make a potion
So you can eat it with many emotions."
                               (Burger's Love Spell)
